---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import pkg from "../../../package.json";
---

<Layout title="VashonMesh - About Us">
  <section class="flex flex-col gap-8">
    <div
      class="bg-[var(--bg-primary)] border border-[var(--border-color)] rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm"
    >
      <h2 class="text-[#667eea] text-2xl mt-0">Welcome</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
        VashonMesh is a small group of rebels informally helping islanders
        connect with MeshCore and related local area mesh networks.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
        Our mission is to empower neighbors to build resilient, decentralized
        networks that foster communication and collaboration.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
        Want to help spread the word? Check out our <a
          href="/vashon-mesh/banners"
          class="text-[#667eea] hover:underline font-medium"
          >promotional banners and marketing materials</a
        > that you can download and share.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] opacity-70 mt-4">
        Website version: {pkg.version}
      </p>
    </div>

    <h3>Intro</h3>
    <p>
      Vashon folks are interested to cooperatively learn about the relatively
      new Lora technology. Incentives range from education, playing with fun
      gadgets, long distance communication with sensors, and especially
      Emergency Communications: EMCOMM.
    </p>
  </section>
  • Experimenting • Activities/Events • Informal group • Other (regional) groups

  <h3>Other Communities</h3>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://meshcore.org"
        class="text-[#667eea] hover:underline font-medium">MeshCore</a
      >
      - Open source software platform for building and managing community mesh networks.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://www.themeshnet.org/"
        class="text-[#667eea] hover:underline font-medium">The Meshnet</a
      >
      - Global community of mesh network enthusiasts sharing knowledge and resources.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://pugetmesh.org/"
        class="text-[#667eea] hover:underline font-medium">PugetMesh</a
      >
      & Discord: https://discord.gg/Y4PddSUd
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://bostonme.sh/"
        class="text-[#667eea] hover:underline font-medium">BostonMesh</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://www.austinmesh.org/"
        class="text-[#667eea] hover:underline font-medium">AustinMesh</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://www.arizonamesh.org/"
        class="text-[#667eea] hover:underline font-medium">ArizonaMesh</a
      >
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <details
      class="border border-[var(--border-color)] rounded-lg bg-[var(--bg-primary)] overflow-hidden faq-item"
      open
    >
      <summary
        class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-3 font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)] transition-colors list-none hover:bg-[var(--hover-bg)]"
      >
        <span>What are the basic features?</span>

        <svg
          width="20"
          height="20"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-5 h-5 max-w-5 max-h-5 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300 arrow"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M12 5v14m0 0l7-7m-7 7l-7-7"></path>
        </svg>
      </summary>

      <div class="p-4">
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Lorem, ipsum dolor sit
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details
      class="border border-[var(--border-color)] rounded-lg bg-[var(--bg-primary)] overflow-hidden faq-item"
      open
    >
      <summary
        class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-3 font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)] transition-colors list-none hover:bg-[var(--hover-bg)]"
      >
        <span>How do I get started?</span>

        <svg
          width="20"
          height="20"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-5 h-5 max-w-5 max-h-5 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300 arrow"
        >
          <path
